description:
This week, I'm back with another American Horror Story Murder House reaction. This week's episode, titled "Murder House," give a bit more backstory about the history of the home. To me, this episode of AHS was incredibly confusing, but I liked it overall! 

If you love American Horror Story, feel free to subscribe to my channel. I'm going to be reacting to the entire first season on my channel!

*There are a few scenes in this episode that can be incredibly triggering, so please watch at your own discretion. I tried to cut out the most graphic parts.
